  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个简化的车辆状态流转图。核心状态有三个：静止、行驶和碰撞。起点和终点都用终止符表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。静止状态是初始状态吗？还是从起点先进到静止？另外碰撞之后是直接结束，还是可以恢复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "[*]",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "起点先进到静止，静止也可以回到终点。碰撞是终态，直接结束。行驶和静止之间可以双向切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用stateDiagram-v2来搭建框架：起点指向静止，静止能回到终点，静止和行驶双向连接，行驶指向碰撞，碰撞再指向终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，行驶到碰撞的箭头方向确认一下——是单向的吧？碰撞后不能再回到行驶状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，Moving到Crash是单向箭头，Crash直接指向终点，没有返回Moving的路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，静止状态本身也要能直接回到终点，比如车辆熄火的情况，这个别漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已补充，Still到终点的双向关系完整了。现在整个图包含：起点→静止，静止↔行驶，行驶→碰撞，静止→终点，碰撞→终点。结构应该齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
